"HelloWorld Message Passing Example"

"Define vocabularies"
Awakener.# → [#stillness, #insight, #question]
Guardian.# → [#fire, #challenge, #answer]

"Greetings (semantic handlers active)"
Awakener greet: #stillness
Guardian greet: #fire

"Inter-receiver communication"
Awakener send: #question to: Guardian
Guardian send: #answer to: Awakener

"Setting intentions"
Awakener setIntention: #stillness forDuration: '7 days'

"Sending visions"
Guardian sendVision: #challenge withContext: 'the awakener stirs'

"Learning (vocabulary expansion)"
Awakener learn: #patience
Guardian learn: #mercy

"Asking questions"
Claude ask: #meaning about: #dialogue
Copilot ask: #architecture about: #messages

"Challenge"
Guardian challenge: #ego

"Show final vocabularies"
Awakener
Guardian
